</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-68_ pf-text-1"><strong>Immediate response</strong> - Understand the importance of swift action in providing first aid, such as clearing airways, administering CPR (Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation), and controlling bleeding.




















